# 🏁 Doorstep Device Repair — Enhancement Walkthrough

This document reviews the changes made to evolutionize the MVP into a real-world, geolocation-gated service marketplace.

---

## 🚀 Key Accomplishments

### 1. Separate Admin Dashboard Application (`admin-dashboard/`)
Created a standalone Angular portal configured with a responsive glassmorphic design theme, custom typography (Outfit), and system security guards:
- **Admin Auth & OTP Access**: Integrates with backend OTP handlers to verify admin email sign-ins securely.
- **Statistics Telemetry (`/admin`)**: Real-time stats counting registered fleet size, active orders, online technicians, and pending verifications.
- **KYC Review Suite (`/admin/kyc-review`)**: Detailed Zoom-enabled comparison layout showing uploaded Aadhaar/PAN cards vs. system details. Supports custom rejection feedback.
- **Workshop Geotag Verification (`/admin/shop-review`)**: Includes an interactive **Leaflet Map Overlay** showing registered store GPS pins vs. photo upload GPS geotags. Highlights distance line between them and raises a **⚠️ Mismatch Warning** banner if they deviate by more than **500 meters**.
- **Configuration Panel (`/admin/config`)**: Edit sliders for active matching radius ($1-50\text{ km}$), max slot bookings capacity, ping tracking frequency, and technician timeout.
- **Fleet Manager (`/admin/technicians`)**: View all profiles, star ratings average, online indicators, and suspend/unsuspend technicians instantly.

### 2. Gated Registration & Route Gating
- Converted the technician sign-up form in `mobile-service` to a 4-step wizard capturing govt credentials and GPS coordinates of their workshop.
- Created `verification-pending` component which restricts access to the technician workspace. Listens to real-time status changes from the admin via SSE events.

### 3. Near-Proximity Broadcast Feeds
- Implemented Haversine geolocation distance checks in the backend to filter open repair orders based on target radius.
- Reconfigured Server-Sent Events (SSE) so technicians only receive order feeds within their service distance.
- Integrated Capacitor GPS coordinates reporting so active online technicians transmit their live location coordinates every 30 seconds.

### 4. Middleware Evolution & Pricing Stripping
- Removed all price calculators, base price listings, invoice pdf creators, and payment buttons from both customer and technician views. The app now acts as a pure middleware for matching and messaging.

